# Components Context

When working with files in `src/components/`, read `documentation/components.md` for:
- Component tree hierarchy (UmoEditor → Toolbar + ContainerPage + Statusbar)
- Toolbar menu structure (base, insert, table, tools, page, view, export)
- Bubble menus — which node types have context menus
- Block menu — drag handle
- How to add a new toolbar button or bubble menu
- All components are auto-imported via unplugin-vue-components with directoryAsNamespace
- Data flows via provide/inject, not props — see `documentation/composables-and-state.md`
